detail.name: Trunks : Adolescence
detail.effect: [On Play] Add up to 1 card from your life to your hand. Then, choose up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 1 or less in your opponent's Battle Area and place it at the bottom of its owner's deck.

detail.name: トランクス：青年期
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のライフ1枚までを手札に加える。その後、相手のバトルエリアのコスト1以下のバトルカード1枚までを選び、デッキの下に置く。
